+---
+date: "2026-06-11"
+status: done
+implements: [FR-E83]
+tags: [engine, cli, state, runs, housekeeping]
+related_tasks:
+  - 2026/05/per-workflow-run-lock.md
+  - 2026/05/per-run-worktree-co-location.md
